import React,{useContext} from 'react' import { AppState,DepositState,BalanceState,WithdrawState } from '../App' import './UserInfo.css' const UserInfo = () => { const {userInfo} = useContext(AppState) const {amountDeposit} = useContext(DepositState) const {amountWithdraw} = useContext(WithdrawState) const {amountBalance} = useContext(BalanceState) return (

User Information

Name {userInfo.Fname} {UserInfo.Lname}

Phone {userInfo.phone}

Id {userInfo.id}

Email {userInfo.email}

Deposited Amount {amountDeposit.deposit}

Withdraw Amount {amountWithdraw.withdraw}

Balance {amountBalance.balance}

) } export default UserInfo
